<div class="title">Drinking with Friends</div>
<div class="substance">Alcohol</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Ben&Exact=1">Ben</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Ben. "Drinking with Friends: An Experience with Alcohol (exp54474)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Dec 5, 2007. erowid.org/exp/54474</div>

<br/>



